text:
After Stefani and her parents welcomed Shelton into their family, they asked him to become a Catholic as a final step to the altar. "Blake didn't blink when he was asked," the source revealed. "It's adorable how much Blake wants to make Gwen happy. She's finally getting her fairy-tale ending!"
